  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IJTabs
    A class for the control of the ImageJ tabs.
    ImageMethods
    This class provides some static methods for the analysis and transfer of images inside the Bio7 application.
    Individual
    This class provides some static methods for the creation of individual properties for the use in the Points panel of the Bio7 application.
    PointPanel
    This class provides methods for the Points panel of the Bio7 application and the points attributes inside the Points panel.
